import * as React from 'react';
import Button from '@mui/material/Button';
import Card from '@mui/material/Card';
import CardActions from '@mui/material/CardActions';
import CardContent from '@mui/material/CardContent';
import CardMedia from '@mui/material/CardMedia';
import CssBaseline from '@mui/material/CssBaseline';
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';
import Stack from '@mui/material/Stack';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography';
import Container from '@mui/material/Container';
import Link from '@mui/material/Link';
import BarCharts from '../components/barcharts';
import LineCharts from '../components/linecharts';
import '../components/PieChart.css';
import { FaFileWord, FaFilePdf, FaFileAlt } from 'react-icons/fa';

export default function Album() {
  return (
      
      <main>
        {/* Hero unit */}
        <Box
          sx={{
            bgcolor: 'background.paper',
            pt: 8,
            pb: 6,
          }}
        >
          <Container maxWidth="sm">
            <Typography
              component="h1"
              variant="h3"
              align="center"
              color="text.primary"
              gutterBottom
            >
              Resume
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h5" align="center" color="text.secondary" paragraph>
              Professional front end user interface software application developer with 20 years experience. 
              Architect of new software development, assists product managers with design of new features, 
              also supporting existing customers by transitioning legacy products. Serving the engineering 
              team as scrum master and mentored junior developers to apply my knowledge and skills to 
              learn and contribute to the success of an organization.
            </Typography>
            <Stack
              sx={{ pt: 4 }}
              direction="row"
              spacing={2}
              justifyContent="center"
            >
           
           </Stack>
          </Container>
        </Box>
        <Container sx={{ py: 8 }} maxWidth="md">
          {/* End hero unit */}
          <Grid container spacing={4}>

         

              <Grid item key={1} xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
                <Card
                  sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}
                >
                  
                  <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
                   <Typography
              component="h1"
              variant="h3"
              align="center"
              color="text.primary"
              gutterBottom
            >
                   <FaFilePdf className="resume-icon PDF-icon"/>

                      <Button variant="contained" href="/files/ArinSturm_resume2023.pdf">Resume.PDF</Button>
                   </Typography>
                  </CardContent>
                  
                </Card>
              </Grid>

              <Grid item key={2} xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
                <Card
                  sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}
                >
                  
                  <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
                   <Typography
              component="h1"
              variant="h3"
              align="center"
              color="text.primary"
              gutterBottom
            >
                   <FaFileAlt className="resume-icon Text-icon"/>
                      <Button variant="contained" href="/files/ArinSturm_resume2023.pdf">Resume.TdddXT</Button>
                    </Typography>
                  </CardContent>
                  
                </Card>
              </Grid>

             

   	<Grid item key={3} xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
                <Card
                  sx={{ height: '100%', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column' }}
                >
      	
                  <CardContent sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}>
                   <Typography
              component="h1"
              variant="h3"
              align="center"
              color="text.primary"
              gutterBottom
            >
                  <FaFileWord className="resume-icon Word-icon"/>
                  
                      <Button variant="contained" href="//files/ArinSturm_resume2023.docx">Resume.DOCX</Button>
 </Typography>
                    
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </Grid>

              


          </Grid>
        </Container>
      </main>

  );
}
